{ Welcome chess players! I am Grandmaster Max Illingworth, here to help you improve your rating by 100+ points fast!

What you will learn:

- The Basic Opening Principles for getting a good game;
- The Main Traps To Avoid;
- How To Take Control Of The Game

Coaching Question 1: Let me know (using the chat room to the left): What you think these three opening principles are? }
