{ The Basic Opening Principles Are:

1. Fight For Control Of The Centre (see the highlighted squares d4/d5/e4/e5 in the middle of the board).

Why do we want to control the centre?

Because our pieces have more mobility in the centre of the board. } { [%csl Gd5,Ge5,Ge4,Gd4] }
 *


