{ 3. Get Your King Castled To Safety.

Why is this important?

When our king is in the centre of the board, our king can be attacked from the centre, the left and the right. (see arrows above)

However, when we castle our king, it's much harder for our opponent to threaten our king.

In most cases, they will need to reposition their pieces to the side we have castled if they want to threaten our king. } { [%cal Ga4e8,Gh5e8,Ge4e8] }
 *


